data.description: Welcome home to this great open floor plan with a cozy converted wood fireplace. Split primary bedroom for privacy with an ensuite which you can relax in a spacious garden tub and also has a separate shower. There's another full-size bathroom nestled between two additional bedrooms and either a possible 4th bedroom or perfect for an office. Stainless steel appliances convey in the kitchen which opens up to a breakfast nook and an eat up kitchen bar. Perfect location for quick and easy access to the elementary school, parks, and walking/biking paths that truly make this neighborhood a unique master planned community.
